        `Welcome back! I'll need some details to schedule your visit. What is your First Name and Last Name?`,
        `So happy you're returning! To schedule your appointment, I need some information. What is your First Name and Last Name?`,
        `Welcome back! I'll need a few details to book your appointment. What is your First Name and Last Name?`,
        `Great to see you again! To schedule your appointment, I need some details. What is your First Name and Last Name?`
      ];

      response = getRandomResponse(existingPatientResponses);
